=== Affiliate members ===
;Notes:
* On July 29, 2015, the Big 12 announced it would add the six former members of the Western Wrestling Conference—Air Force, Northern Colorado, North Dakota State, South Dakota State, Utah Valley, and Wyoming—as affiliate members for wrestling, plus Denver as an affiliate member for women&#x27;s gymnastics, all effective with the 2015–16 academic year.
* On July 5, 2017, the Big 12 added Fresno State and Northern Iowa as wrestling affiliates.
* On May 2, 2019, the Big 12 added Fresno State as an equestrian affiliate. Fresno State would drop wrestling in 2021, but remains an equestrian affiliate.
* In 2021, the Big 12 added former full member Missouri as a wrestling affiliate.

