* Tracks 10–15 are the January 3, 1966, Factory rehearsals, also from tape, previously unreleased.

==Charts==
==Certifications==

According to Nielsen SoundScan, which tracks sales, &quot;The Velvet Underground &amp; Nico&quot; has sold 560,000 copies since 1991.

